478
01:12:13.515 --> 01:12:17.383
<i>You have to say "Yes. yes. yes" to
any selfish demands they make.</i>

479
01:12:17.519 --> 01:12:19.453
<i>They demand ridiculous things.</i>

480
01:12:19.588 --> 01:12:21.783
<i>Shut up... Do you know what would
happen if they heard you?</i>

481
01:12:21.924 --> 01:12:24.290
<i>- What's gonna happen?
- Did you hear about the Tanaka clan?</i>

482
01:12:24.426 --> 01:12:26.188
<i>You're gonna get your head
chopped off.</i>

483
01:12:26.327 --> 01:12:28.056
<i>No. I don't want that.</i>

484
01:13:15.276 --> 01:13:16.800
<i>Yes. it's me.</i>

485
01:13:20.680 --> 01:13:24.013
<i>And if you give us a contact number.
we will get back to you.</i>

486
01:13:37.164 --> 01:13:39.257
Hey. You!

487
01:13:39.633 --> 01:13:42.534
<i>Who do you remind me of?</i>

488
01:13:43.270 --> 01:13:45.204
<i>Charlie Brown!</i>

489
01:13:46.139 --> 01:13:48.801
<i>You're right. he does look like
Charlie Brown.</i>

490
01:13:48.942 --> 01:13:51.843
<i>Charlie Brown.
Four pepperonu pizzas.</i>

491
01:13:51.978 --> 01:13:56.005
<i>- That's not on our menu...
- I don't care. bring them. goddammit!</i>

492
01:13:56.917 --> 01:13:59.818
<i>Hey... hey...
Charlie. give me a kiss.</i>

493
01:14:01.321 --> 01:14:03.255
<i>O-Ren Ishii!</i>

494
01:14:04.291 --> 01:14:06.919
<i>You and I have unfinished business!</i>

495
01:15:37.415 --> 01:15:40.475
<i>Charlie Brown. beat it.</i>

496
01:15:47.926 --> 01:15:49.052
<i>Miki</i>

497
01:16:07.344 --> 01:16:09.039
<i>TEAR THE BITCH APART!</i>

498
01:17:41.904 --> 01:17:43.337
So. O-Ren...

499
01:17:44.573 --> 01:17:47.410
...any more subordinated
for me to kill?

500
01:17:49.011 --> 01:17:50.239
Hi.

501
01:17:51.914 --> 01:17:53.437
<i>Gogo. right?</i>

502
01:17:54.883 --> 01:17:58.284
<i>Bingo.
And you're Black Mamba.</i>

503
01:18:00.255 --> 01:18:03.622
<i>Our reputations precede us.</i>

504
01:18:04.726 --> 01:18:06.091
<i>Don't they?</i>

505
01:18:08.029 --> 01:18:09.189
Gogo...

506
01:18:10.065 --> 01:18:13.159
...I know you feel you must protect
your mistress...

507
01:18:14.302 --> 01:18:15.701
...but I beg you.

508
01:18:17.005 --> 01:18:18.267
...walk away.

509
01:18:25.580 --> 01:18:27.571
<i>You call that begging?</i>

510
01:18:33.621 --> 01:18:35.919
<i>You can beg better than that.</i>

511
01:21:50.347 --> 01:21:51.780
Is that what I think it is?

512
01:21:51.916 --> 01:21:54.680
You didn't think it would be that easy.
did you?

513
01:21:55.319 --> 01:21:58.447
You know.
for a second there...

514
01:21:58.889 --> 01:22:01.722
...yeah. I kind of did.

515
01:22:03.160 --> 01:22:04.821
"Silly rabbit."

516
01:22:05.596 --> 01:22:07.393
"Trix are for kids."

517
01:29:01.403 --> 01:29:05.362
This is what you get for fucking
around with the yakuzas.

518
01:29:06.041 --> 01:29:07.565
Go home to your mother!

519
01:30:06.567 --> 01:30:12.028
<i>Those of you lucky enough to still
have your lives take them with you!</i>

520
01:30:13.775 --> 01:30:15.003
<i>However...</i>

521
01:30:16.411 --> 01:30:20.507
<i>... leave the limbs you've lost.</i>

522
01:30:21.516 --> 01:30:24.917
<i>They belong to me now.</i>

523
01:30:29.824 --> 01:30:32.258
Except you. Sofie!

524
01:30:33.027 --> 01:30:36.053
You stay right where you are.

525
01:31:29.749 --> 01:31:32.047
Your instrument is quite imressive.

526
01:31:36.789 --> 01:31:38.552
<i>Where was it made?</i>

527
01:31:40.359 --> 01:31:41.587
Okinawa.

528
01:31:43.762 --> 01:31:46.890
<i>Whom in Okinawa made you this steel?</i>

529
01:31:48.100 --> 01:31:49.431
This is Hattori Hanzo steel.

530
01:31:49.802 --> 01:31:51.497
<i>YOU LIE!</i>

531
01:32:04.116 --> 01:32:06.607
<i>Swords however. never get tired.</i>

532
01:32:07.653 --> 01:32:11.521
<i>I hope you've saved your energy.</i>

533
01:32:14.827 --> 01:32:16.294
<i>If you haven't...</i>

534
01:32:18.130 --> 01:32:20.462
<i>... you might not last five minutes.</i>

535
01:32:22.201 --> 01:32:24.635
<i>But as last looks go.</i>

536
01:32:25.538 --> 01:32:27.164
<i>you could do worse.</i>

537
01:35:06.328 --> 01:35:10.788
Silly Caucasian girl likes to play
with samurai swords.

538
01:35:13.134 --> 01:35:15.830
You may not be able to fight
like a samurai...

539
01:35:19.240 --> 01:35:21.936
...but you can at least die
like a samurai.

540
01:35:52.574 --> 01:35:54.439
<i>Attack me...</i>

541
01:35:55.276 --> 01:35:56.937
<i>... with everything you have.</i>

542
01:36:52.199 --> 01:36:54.895
<i>For ridiculing you earlier...</i>

543
01:36:57.437 --> 01:36:59.166
<i>... I apologize.</i>

544
01:37:08.014 --> 01:37:09.538
<i>Accepted.</i>

545
01:37:25.798 --> 01:37:27.095
<i>Ready?</i>

546
01:37:31.804 --> 01:37:32.964
<i>Come on.</i>

547
01:38:06.204 --> 01:38:15.078
<i>That really was a Hattori Hanzo sword.</i>

548
01:40:21.337 --> 01:40:22.497
Sofie.

549
01:40:23.606 --> 01:40:24.903
Sofie.

550
01:40:25.441 --> 01:40:29.138
My Sofie. I'm so sorry.

551
01:40:32.949 --> 01:40:36.316
Please. Please forgive my betrayal.

552
01:40:36.452 --> 01:40:37.783
No more of that.

553
01:40:38.454 --> 01:40:39.681
But still...

554
01:40:40.355 --> 01:40:42.687
But still nothing...

555
01:40:44.559 --> 01:40:46.618
...except my aching heart...

556
01:40:46.762 --> 01:40:50.892
...over what she's done to my
beautiful and brilliant Sofie.

557
01:40:51.967 --> 01:40:54.561
I've kept you alive for two reasons.

558
01:40:54.970 --> 01:40:57.268
First reason is information.

559
01:40:57.406 --> 01:41:02.503
<i>Burn in Hell you stupid. stupid blonde!
I'll tell you nothing.</i>

560
01:41:04.012 --> 01:41:07.504
But I'm going to ask you questions.

561
01:41:08.283 --> 01:41:11.844
And every time you don't give me
answers...

562
01:41:12.387 --> 01:41:14.855
...I'm going to cut something off.

563
01:41:15.791 --> 01:41:17.782
And I promise you...

564
01:41:18.160 --> 01:41:21.527
...they will be things you will miss.

565
01:41:23.198 --> 01:41:24.722
Give me your other arm!

566
01:41:37.111 --> 01:41:41.775
<i>I want all the information on
the Deadly Vipers.</i>

567
01:41:41.916 --> 01:41:43.941
<i>- If you had to guess...
- What they've been doing...</i>

568
01:41:44.085 --> 01:41:47.282
<i>- ...Why she left you alive...
- ...and where I can find them.</i>

569
01:41:47.421 --> 01:41:49.286
...what would be your guess?

570
01:41:51.425 --> 01:41:53.586
Guessing won't be necessary.

571
01:41:54.295 --> 01:41:55.990
She informed me.

572
01:41:58.432 --> 01:42:02.163
She said I could keep my wicked life
for two reasons.

573
01:42:03.370 --> 01:42:04.496
<i>As i said before...</i>

574
01:42:04.638 --> 01:42:08.802
...I've allowed you to keep your
wicked life for two reasons.

575
01:42:09.477 --> 01:42:11.741
And the second reason is...

576
01:42:11.979 --> 01:42:17.440
...so you can tell him. in person
everything that happened here tonight.

577
01:42:18.752 --> 01:42:21.983
I want him to witness the extent of
my mercy...

578
01:42:22.123 --> 01:42:24.921
...by witnessing your deformed body.

579
01:42:25.826 --> 01:42:29.693
I want you to tell him all
the information you just told me.

580
01:42:30.063 --> 01:42:32.827
I want him to know what I know.

581
01:42:33.199 --> 01:42:36.828
I want him to know I want him to know.

582
01:42:37.470 --> 01:42:39.995
And I want them all to know...

583
01:42:40.140 --> 01:42:45.442
...they'll all soon be as dead as O-Ren.

584
01:43:09.836 --> 01:43:15.035
<i>Revenge is never a straight line.</i>

585
01:43:17.710 --> 01:43:19.439
<i>It's a forest.</i>

586
01:43:20.647 --> 01:43:23.479
<i>And like a forest
it's easy to lose your way...</i>

587
01:43:24.783 --> 01:43:28.219
<i>... to get lost...
to forget where you came in.</i>

588
01:43:31.523 --> 01:43:32.820
That woman...

589
01:43:33.492 --> 01:43:35.551
...deserves her revenge.

590
01:43:40.699 --> 01:43:41.927
And...

591
01:43:42.901 --> 01:43:44.960
...we deserve to die.

592
01:43:48.473 --> 01:43:51.965
She must suffer to her last breath.

593
01:44:05.190 --> 01:44:06.851
How did you find me?

594
01:44:08.193 --> 01:44:09.558
I'm the man.

595
01:44:13.932 --> 01:44:15.923
One more thing. Sofie.

596
01:44:17.402 --> 01:44:21.269
Is she aware her daughter
is still alive?

597
01:44:22.305 --> 01:45:22.339
Do you want subtitles for any video?
